OL,3,CFamily robbed of three generations by
OL,4,COmagh atrocity 'hope no others suffer'
OL,6,FThe Omagh Bombing Inquiry has heard
OL,7,Fthat the unborn twin girls murdered in
OL,8,Fthe atrocity were later named.
OL,10,FThe Monaghan family lost three
OL,11,Fgenerations in the real IRA attack in
OL,12,Fthe Co Tyrone town in 1998.
OL,14,FThe Inquiry is examining if the
OL,15,Fbombing could have been prevented. The
OL,16,Fsecond day of hearings focused on the
OL,17,Fvery youngest children and their
OL,18,Ffamilies.
