OL,6,FMary Grimes died in the atrocity on
OL,7,Fher 66th birthday, along with her
OL,8,Fdaughter Avril Monaghan, 30, who was
OL,9,Fpregnant with twin daughters, and her
OL,10,F20-month-old daughter Maura.
OL,12,FThe Omagh Bombing Inquiry heard
OL,13,Ftributes to them during the second day
OL,14,Fof commemorative hearings for the 29
OL,15,Fvictims of the August 15, 1998
OL,16,Fdissident republican bomb attack.
OL,18,FInquiry chair Lord Turnbull described
OL,19,Fan "incomprehensible loss".
