OL,6,FThe inquiry was shown photographs of
OL,7,FMrs Grimes, Mrs Monaghan and little
OL,8,FMaura ` who won a "bonnie baby"
OL,9,Fcompetition during her short life, as
OL,10,Fwell as ultrasound scan pictures of
OL,11,Fthe unborn twin girls who had been
OL,12,Fnamed Eimear and Evelyn.
OL,14,FFearghal Grimes gave evidence to the
OL,15,Finquiry on Wednesday. He recalled how
OL,16,Fat the inquests into the Omagh bomb,
OL,17,Fformer senior coroner John Leckey said
OL,18,Fhe could not recall any one family
OL,19,Fsuffering such a loss in the history
OL,20,Fof the Troubles.
