OL,3,CFamily robbed of three generations by
OL,4,COmagh atrocity 'hope no others suffer'
OL,6,F"A massive dignified crowd at her wake
OL,7,Fand funeral and those of her beautiful
OL,8,Fdaughter Avril, her granddaughter
OL,9,FMaura and Avril's unborn twins
OL,10,Freflected the enormity of the loss for
OL,11,Fher family, neighbours and society."
OL,13,FHe added: "Were it not for the faith
OL,14,Fand compassion that our mother Mary
OL,15,Fand father Mick passed on to us 11
OL,16,Fchildren and 28 grandchildren and
OL,17,Findeed the local community, we would
OL,18,Fnot have been fit to carry on with the
OL,19,Fquiet dignity and resolve to make
OL,20,Fsociety a better place for everyone."
