OL,6,FIn a recording played to the inquiry,
OL,7,FMrs Monaghan's daughter Aoibheann
OL,8,Fspoke about her mother Avril, sister
OL,9,FMaura and the two twin girls she had
OL,10,Flooked forward to having as sisters.
OL,12,FShe described Maura as a "source of
OL,13,Flight and joy to our family and
OL,14,Feveryone around her", with a "bubbly
OL,15,Fpersonality and unmistakable head of
OL,16,Fcurly hair".
OL,26,@tD@ZOUvD@TO]vD@^OUxD@KO]
