OL,6,FShe said she had become the proud
OL,7,Fmother of four children by the age of
OL,8,F30, describing her as "calm and
OL,9,Fnurturing and approached life with a
OL,10,Fcan-do attitude".
OL,12,F"Her life at the age of 30 was
OL,13,Ftragically cut short on August 15,
OL,14,F1998," she said.
