OL,6,FShe described the twin girls as two
OL,7,Flittle girls they were extremely
OL,8,Fexcited to meet and welcome.
OL,10,FShe said: "Unfortunately that day did
OL,11,Fnot come, and the pictures of the scan
OL,12,Fare a reminder of the many futures
OL,13,Fthat never became a reality following
OL,14,Fthe bomb on August 15, 1998."
OL,16,FShe added: "We have no doubt that
OL,17,Fmummy, Maura, Eimear, Evelyn and
OL,18,Fgranny have been our guardian angels
OL,19,Fover the years and will continue to be
OL,20,Fpresent in our lives for all time.
OL,26,@rD@KOUvD@]O]xD@LOU
