OL,3,CFamily robbed of three generations by
OL,4,COmagh atrocity 'hope no others suffer'
OL,6,F"The loss we as a family have
OL,7,Fexperienced over the last 26 years
OL,8,Fcannot be measured, and there is no
OL,9,Freplacement for the time we would have
OL,10,Fhad with mummy, Maura, Eimear, Evelyn
OL,11,Fand granny.
OL,13,F"We are however eternally grateful for
OL,14,Fthe time that we did have with them,
OL,15,Fand we only hope that no other family
OL,16,Fhas to suffer as we did."
